Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:06.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Like an angel that has no\Nsense of mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:13.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Rise, young boy, to the heavens\Nlike a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Cold winds, as blue as the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Tear open the door to\Nyour heart, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But unknowing you seem, just\Nstaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:37.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Standing there smiling serenely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Desperate, for something to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,A moment of kindness like\Nthat in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:51.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Of the path your destiny will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But someday you’ll become aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Everything that you’ve got behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:03.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your wings are for seeking out a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Future that only you can search for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:14.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis enters through\Nthe window of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:18.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,If you should betray the chapel\Nof your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis bleeds through\Na portal like your pulsing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,So, boy, stand tall and embrace\Nthe fire of the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:29.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Embracing the universe like\Na blazing star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cool!  I won a free ice cream bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:52.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Boy, the cost of doing laundry has\Nbeen killing me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:56.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just wish I had the time to wash\Nmy clothes for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You should appreciate the fact that\Nyou can at least sleep at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello, Vice-Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good morning, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re quite early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I have to go uptown as\NIkari’s representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see, isn’t today the City Council’s\Nregular meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s a boring job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He always forces the most\Ntedious work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Without the MAGI’s help,\NI couldn’t do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, election day\Nis coming up, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The City Council has no\Nauthority at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Actually, the MAGI run\Neverything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The MAGI?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean the three\Nsupercomputers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Government by the majority decision\Nof three different computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s a sort of democratic system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And the council just obeys\Ntheir decisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s a most effective form\Nof government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This truly is a “city of science.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We are fortunate to live in an\Nera when Almighty Science\Nreigns supreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Talk about old fashioned viewpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:11.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you have\Nan experiment to run on\NUnit 00, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:16.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, we’re going to perform\Nthe second prolonged activation\Ntest at 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m expecting good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Abort experiment!  Cut the circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switching circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Power supply restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This component is the\Nproblem again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:39.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think the problem is the conversion\Nefficiency is 0.008 lower than our\Ntheoretical calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s within the tolerance\Nthough, barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s try it again using the\Nsame configuration...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but lower the reciprocal\Nconversion rate by 0.01.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, let’s recommence the\Nreactivation experiment.
