Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:05.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man, I’ve never had to\Nrun this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So what’s with the black expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s from having to see your\Nloathsome face first thing\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, hold just a moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?  Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:48.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...tell my parent that an interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:54.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...for Advanced Vocational\NEducation is going to be\Nheld at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:59.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve delegated things like\Nthat to Captain Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t bother me with such nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t forward any more\Nof these calls to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:08.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, it can’t be.  It’s not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Something’s strange.  An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Perhaps Dr. Akagi made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The main power supply has\Nbeen interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Voltage level is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’ll switch to the backup\Npower supply soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, the backup circuits\Naren’t working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That can’t be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Which circuits are functioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Only 1.2% of them!\NOnly nine circuits out of 2,567!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Route all of the remaining power\Ncircuits to maintain the MAGI\Nand Central Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But that could interfere with\Nlife support systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do it!  That’s our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is Nozomu Takahashi, who\Nwants a more cheerful government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Boy, she’s such a lazy slob.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}This is Nozomu Takahashi, who\Nwants a more cheerful government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Boy, she’s such a lazy slob.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}We need your support for this\Nrighteous and honest candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:04.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Can’t she pick up her own laundry?\N{\c&H00E3FE&}We need your support for this\Nrighteous and honest candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:12.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maybe Commander Ikari was\Njust really busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:17.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It wasn’t like he hung up.  It was\Nmore like a mechanical failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, are you a man or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stop letting every little\Nincident bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you think you’re doing?\NHere, let me try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn!!  It must be broken, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Heave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’d better head for the\Ncommand station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been seven minutes and the\Npower hasn’t restored itself.  This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s the backup\Npower system here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There are three circuits,\Nmain, sub and reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s virtually impossible for all\Nof those to fail at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:11.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the circuit breakers didn’t go on\Ntheir own.  Someone must have\Nblown them intentionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Regardless of the cause, it would be\Ndisastrous if an Angel were to\Nattack right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Radar has detected an\Nunidentified object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Projected landing point is in\Nthe former Atami region.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It must be number eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I agree, it must be an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go to alert status.  That’s the\Nprocedure, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This one’s destination\Nhas to be Tokyo-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I agree.  Well, this is no job for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angel has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s still advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about Tokyo-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s still silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What in the hell are those\NNERV guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:57.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I never thought I’d actually have to\Nuse one of these trap exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thought they were just holdovers\Nfrom an outdated technology that\Nwe kept for our peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,“To provide is to prevent.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This one doesn’t work either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,None of the facilities work.\NThis is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Could this mean that something’s\Nhappened down in the Geo-Front?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It is natural to assume that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In any case, let’s try to make contact\Nwith NERV Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, the emergency phones aren’t\Ngetting through either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, there’s no answer on Line 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not on this one either.\NSo, the main and emergency\Ncables are both down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’re you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:46.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?  I’m looking\Nfor my emergency manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anyway, let’s go to\NNERV Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:53.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, but before that we’ll need\Nto decide who will be the\Nleader of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And naturally, I am the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can proceed along\NRoute-07, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the doors don’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can open it manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There you go, Shinji, that’s your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t believe it!  You always\Nwant to control everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but you always defer to me\Nin a situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:25.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn those Joint Staff Council\Nbastards!  They always defer\Nto us in a situation like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What does the government say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those Tokyo-2 buttheads?\NThey’re getting ready to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angel is still advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In any case, we must contact NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,By going there yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the 3rd District ASDF!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An unidentified object is moving\Ntoward this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All residents must evacuate to\Ntheir designated shelters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got to report this\Nto headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Remember Takahashi, who remains\Ncalm even in situations\Nsuch as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please support candidate Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, the air conditioners are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you’re so hot, why don’t you\Ntake off your shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s no reason for shyness\Nbetween you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t even think about trying to\Ntake advantage of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:32.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s getting even worse.\NNow, the air is getting stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s hard to believe that this facility\Nrepresents the most advanced\Ntechnology on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But look at the Commander\Nand Vice-Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Even in this much heat,\Nthey’re cool and in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s getting warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...along with the declaration of\Nemergency in this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Emergency vehicle!\NPassing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, my!  Excuse me, it’s blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s okay!  Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!\NEverything is permitted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Let me off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:21.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This Geo-Front was designed\Nto be a self-sufficient colony, even\Nwhen isolated from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:26.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Theoretically, it’s impossible for all\Nof the power sources to be shut\Ndown at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean that someone\Ncaused it to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Their purpose would be\Nto map this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean they could determine\Nour headquarters’ structure by\Nanalyzing the restoration process?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Disrespectful bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll run a dummy program\Nthrough the MAGI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That will make it harder for them\Nto get a complete picture\Nof the structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:43.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll leave it to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yes, sir.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}I’ll leave it to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yes, sir.\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe the first havoc\Nwreaked upon our headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:51.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...wasn’t caused by some Angel,\Nbut by another member of\Nour own species.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,One of mankind’s greatest enemies\Nis man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But it usually only takes\Ntwo minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:03.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course I’m sure!  If we can\Nget beyond this point we’ll\Nbe at the Geo-Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Haven’t I heard that four\Ntimes already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:11.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re too picky.  You’re always\Nfocusing on the most insubstantial\Nlittle tidbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Silence, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What now, Wonder Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A man’s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ang...  ...proaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s Hyuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey!!  Hey!!  Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:30.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An Angel is approaching!\NRepeat, an Angel is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can’t waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s take a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, I’m the leader!  Don’t take any\Ninitiatives without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now then, where is this shortcut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This may be the quickest way,\Nbut we look really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Say, just what do you think\Nthe Angels are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are you talking about\Nsomething like that at a\Ntime like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:56.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, angels are messengers of God,\Nright?  But our enemies are\Nnamed after angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, why are we fighting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:02.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?\NStrange beings started attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,When someone’s attacking you,\Nyou can’t just sit there and do\Nnothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think the correct path is to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stop bothering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!  I’m the leader, so just\Nshut up and follow me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know, I kind of expected that\Nthis would be a little odd.\NThe path is going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean “you expected”?\NYou’re always nit-picking\Nand worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Look, this has got to be it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we’ve visually confirmed\Nthe Angel’s presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, we know we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An Angel is approaching!\NAn immediate Eva dispatch will\Nbe necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki, take care of\Nthe rest of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I will help prepare for the\Nlaunch in the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean by hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have a diesel generator\Nfor such emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have no pilots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve heard that you’re the\NCommander’s favorite, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re a favored smart ass who’s\Ntreated differently from the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stop it!  This isn’t the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve always got that smug\Nlook on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:57.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think you can\Nact superior just because\Nyou’re treated better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t act superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And I’m not treated better either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know that quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:18.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.  The ejection of the\Ntermination plug is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good, prepare to insert\Nthe entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the pilots aren’t here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, they’ll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s no way I can open\Nthis with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:35.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.  We’ll have to\Nbreak into a duct to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:40.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This First Child isn’t someone to\Nmess with.  She’ll do anything to\Naccomplish her objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s a real self-righteous bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The plug is fixed and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, we just have to\Nwait for the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you dare look forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...I’ll kill you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ignoramus!  Nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have to see to go forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Prepare for entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger, open the hatches manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How are the Evas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re in standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How?  Nothing’s working.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was all done by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was the Commander’s idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My father’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:44.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari believed in you,\NShinji, and prepared everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Plugs inserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All units activated using backup\Npower supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Remove primary lockbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hydraulic locks numbers 2\Nthrough 32, released.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Zero pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The situation is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:18.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go ahead and remove the restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Begin the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The target has stopped\Nright above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Get ready!  Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The emergency batteries\Nhave been installed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we’re ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Launch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Jeez!  I look so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re approaching a vertical shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is still pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Watch out!  Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:08.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It would appear the target is going to\Ninvade headquarters directly using\Nthat liquid solvent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’ll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re going to beat it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sure, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We dropped our rifles and the\Nbattery packs on our backs\Nare running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They won’t last more than\Nanother three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,One of us will take the defensive\Nposition and stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Their job is to neutralize\Nthe Angel’s AT Field...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and to protect the offensive\Nplayer from that acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The backup player...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...will go down, pick up the rifles and\Nhand them to the offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:36.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The offense will then fire a volley\Nto destroy the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see, I will take the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it’s not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:50.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll feel bad if I don’t pay you back\Nfor the one I owe you from\Nthe last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji will be the offense.\NWonder Girl is the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:54.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,CHARGE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ayanami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, get out of the way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now we’re even.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:49.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, damn it!!  Why doesn’t it open?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:54.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a desperate situation!  I’ve got\Nto go to the bathroom now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you not to look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay!  Yes, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s ironic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:24.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Without electricity and artificial\Nlight, the sky can look so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:28.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But without the lights, it’s as if\Nthere were no humans there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:35.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,See?  I feel much more\Ncomfortable this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man has always feared the darkness,\Nso he scrapes away at its edges\Nwith fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:40.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He creates life by diminishing\Nthe darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A philosopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that what makes mankind\Na special species?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that why the Angels keep\Nattacking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:51.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who knows what they think?
